spec_data.Name: alsa-plugins-jack
spec_data.Description:
This plugin converts the ALSA API over JACK (Jack Audio Connection
Kit, http://jackit.sf.net) API.  ALSA native applications can work
transparently together with jackd for both playback and capture.
This plugin provides the PCM type "jack"
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Tue 14 Nov 2017 04:49:05 AM EST, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Jack PCM output plugin for ALSA
